Package: orthodrc
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Yangambi aerial imagery manuscript
Description: Package and data repository for the Yangambi aerial imagery
  recovery manuscript. Serves to assure proper package dependencies and provide 
  a data repository for (some of) the data. To access the full repository 
  you are required to fork or download the github repository.
URL: https://github.com/khufkens/orthodrc
